    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7472174/" class="title-link">刘瑜：在恐惧与热爱之间</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7472174"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/67708717/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u67708717-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/67708717/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">lansingwhere</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-05-14"
      class="main-meta">2015-05-14 06:38:50</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7472174_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一 　　关于什么是好的政治、什么是坏的政治，一百个人可能就有一百个看法，不同阵营之间甚至常常为此争得你死我活。然而，对于什么是好的人性、什么是坏的人性，却一定程度上存在 “普世价值”—一般来说，人们都珍视诚实、友爱、善良、勇敢与忠诚等等品质，同时鄙弃谎言、冷...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7472174_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7472174_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





